Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.36,0:00:20.77,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:23.07,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.07,0:00:29.89,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.20,0:00:40.51,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:43.98,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:49.52,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between\Nthe sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:55.74,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:01:02.75,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good\Ntime just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:07.08,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:09.34,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:16.28,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.49,0:01:26.98,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:30.23,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:35.78,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.09,0:01:41.99,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing,\Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:49.04,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave\Nthe rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:53.53,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.53,0:01:55.74,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.74,0:02:00.08,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.08,0:02:02.85,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:04.87,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.87,0:02:06.62,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.62,0:02:08.19,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:09.85,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:11.47,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.47,0:02:12.98,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:14.64,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.64,0:02:15.71,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:19.91,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:22.20,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:26.65,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.65,0:02:29.00,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:33.19,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.19,0:02:35.54,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.54,0:02:39.51,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:42.67,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy is heading to the \NGreat Prison - Impel Down
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to rescue his brother Ace, who's \Nbeen captured by the navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, his friends have \Nbeen sent to separate islands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Friends' Whereabouts! An Island \Nof Giant Birds and a Pink Paradise!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.61,0:04:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have to tell you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My shin! You kicked my shin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why couldn't you get it, you blockhead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I require at least 100 \Nkilograms of food per meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything less than that won't suffice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to be turned to stone again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! I'm very sorry! I'll be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring her another meal to replace this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Luffy! Bon app√©tit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.59,0:04:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's extremely delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm fed by you, the food tastes \Nsweeter than it actually is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.36,0:04:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...A-And that's how it'd all play out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.90,0:05:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing over there in the corner?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you gonna eat? This \NSea King ham is good as hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I'm okay! You eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally satisfied as I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I can't see anything. \NThe curtain's closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's totally covered! Oh, \Nthere's an open space here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.26,0:05:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love-Love Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.04,0:05:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.69,0:05:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were two bad-mannered rats \Nso I just taught them a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.09,0:05:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:05:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.86,0:05:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be a warning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we ever try to look into her \Nroom, she'll do this to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.90,0:06:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.85,0:06:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, a few days ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.77,0:06:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On an island in the South Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.84,0:06:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't anybody here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they kill them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be it! I won't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.43,0:06:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't scared at all when you guys \Nweren't there. I really wasn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.32,0:07:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! Stop it, Luffy, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.79,0:07:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said stop, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:08:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these birds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.38,0:08:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna eat me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't move my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.63,0:08:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my head is spinning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.94,0:08:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.07,0:08:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.64,0:08:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me this is a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not your toy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.67,0:09:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.65,0:09:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there anybody here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.48,0:09:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thirsty and hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.64,0:10:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only Luffy and everybody else were here,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even on a deserted island like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'd have a banquet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.36,0:10:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Banquet, banquet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll never see them again...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.35,0:10:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is everybody?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.05,0:10:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy... Everybody...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.62,0:10:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made a promise to meet up \Nwhere this Vivre Card leads us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and others will be there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that nothing can stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd eat anything to survive \Nto see everybody again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This fruit is bitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.52,0:11:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's juicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one's too sour!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.52,0:11:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha! I need some meat, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.26,0:11:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this doesn't look so appetizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.26,0:11:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't expect too \Nmuch on a deserted island.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! You can't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell... hit me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.64,0:11:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I gonna be dinner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's so rare to find a raccoon! \NWe'll cook raccoon hot pot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I rather get some birds \Nand do chicken hot pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.29,0:12:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We would've done it, if it were that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.63,0:12:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just have raccoon for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.51,0:12:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! I'm a reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it looks like we'll \Nhave reindeer hot pot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.86,0:12:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh wait, did it just say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do reindeers speak?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go! Just let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's a crisis! We tried to \Nsneak into the birds' nest
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.18,0:12:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they caught us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The birds are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.03,0:13:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's shoo them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.53,0:13:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Let's go, everyone!\N--Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Wait! Set me free before you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the birds are stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Augh! Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.77,0:13:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.03,0:13:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those birds treated me like a toy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.22,0:13:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the humans tried to eat me in a hot pot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with this island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.11,0:13:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One legend suggests this \Nisland is a treasure island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.32,0:13:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Birdie Kingdom, \Nwhere birds reign supreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.85,0:14:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is Chopper's fate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behold! A dream island in the Grand Line
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,called Peachy Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.94,0:14:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Dear Nami-san, Robin-chan,"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"how are you both doing?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Right now, I'm... I'm..."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:50.32,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,- A FEW HOURS BEFORE -
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.47,0:15:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! This is all because of that Warlord!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me! Mister! Mister! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister! Mister! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.72,0:15:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel something... \Nand smell something sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.22,0:15:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the hands of a beautiful woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it... Nami-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.67,0:15:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, is it Robin-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.05,0:15:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I must be dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:16:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's doesn't matter. I \Njust wanna be here forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.19,0:16:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, w-wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.74,0:16:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You forgot your handkerchief! Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it wasn't a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elizabeth?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.76,0:16:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, where the hell am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that I'm in heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.30,0:16:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is Elizabeth...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is heaven,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.84,0:17:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is she an angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.01,0:17:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my heart aches!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.60,0:17:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is my heart beating so fast?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.39,0:17:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.58,0:17:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,must be love!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see that romance is blooming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.09,0:17:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.19,0:17:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.29,0:17:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.31,0:17:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san and Robin-chan are waiting for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.47,0:17:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta say thank you to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.17,0:17:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the kind of guy \Nto forget his manners!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.57,0:17:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me for being unfaithful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.27,0:17:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elizabeth-chan! Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This house has the same \Ndesign as this handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.32,0:18:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, maybe this is Elizabeth's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Lady Elizabeth here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Sanji. You were \Nlooking after me a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here to return your handkerchief...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a bit cruel, Elizabeth-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't rush it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a shy, naive girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got to be cool - have patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry about the \Nway I acted back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.23,0:18:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your hand was so attractive \NI couldn't help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:18:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me for being so forward but
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,may I make it up by cooking \Nsomething for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.37,0:19:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell me whatever you want to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may not look it, but I'm a good chef!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, this isn't working.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like to cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.81,0:19:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes! I love cooking!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, do you like clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike some stupid swordsmen, \NI care about how I look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? You like clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.45,0:19:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about dresses?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dresses?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.94,0:19:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.62,0:19:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She keeps asking what I like because she...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she has a thing for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.49,0:19:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's this dress? Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.41,0:19:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like dresses! I like them! I love them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really fond of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about flower prints?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.75,0:20:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flower prints! They're wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are really cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.59,0:20:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.72,0:20:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, the door to \NElizabeth-chan's heart has...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a good taste, Elizabeth-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be shy! You've already \Nopened up the door of your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.80,0:20:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, don't be afraid and \Njust come into my arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elizabeth-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this will look good on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:20:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.50,0:21:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite your appearance, you're \Nvery strong, Elizabeth-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is this a dream? Then it must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.60,0:21:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that you were one of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.30,0:21:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were suffering, weren't you? \NYou don't have to pretend anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.20,0:21:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is a free country!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.40,0:22:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, put this dress on and open \Nup the door of your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I don't wanna open anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.54,0:22:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.81,0:22:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This island is known as \Nthe second Maiden Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.04,0:22:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is pink here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.77,0:22:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All people and animals \Nwho come to this island
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.60,0:22:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have girlish hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.95,0:22:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.37,0:22:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.79,0:22:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Aren't you one of us?!\N--You are one of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.79,0:22:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Don't come after \Nme! I told you I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.48,0:22:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Dear Nami-san, Robin-chan,"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.96,0:22:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"how are you both doing?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.84,0:22:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Right now, I'm..."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.97,0:22:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm..."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.60,0:22:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm..."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.02,0:22:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm..."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.10,0:23:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wait!\N--Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.11,0:23:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you wait, man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.56,0:23:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I? Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.48,0:23:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to Kamabakka Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.86,0:23:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Right now, I'm..."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.37,0:23:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...in hell!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.37,0:23:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a certain land where snow silently falls,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.83,0:23:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the people have been forced to \Nwork day and night for 700 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.76,0:23:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What has Robin seen there?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.97,0:23:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Around the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.47,0:23:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp is about to be eaten \Nby mysterious plants!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.14,0:23:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.43,0:23:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Friends' Whereabouts! Bridging \Nthe Islands and Vicious Vegetations!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.23,0:23:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
